Dialog Mission Statement These are the dialogs for Crattis Yurkal, one of the merchants in the Jedi Enclave. He comments on the results of plots and offers to buy lightsaber crystals from the player, but otherwise does nothing other than be a store.
The first dialog is the first time the player talks to him before becoming an apprentice. The second dialog is the first time the player talks to him after becoming an apprentice. The third dialog is subsequent conversations before becoming a Padawan. The fourth dialog is Crattis asking the player to get him lightsaber crystals. This happens after the player has been told to find a crystal, but before returning to Zhar with one. The fifth dialog is the first time the player talks to him after becoming a Padawan. The sixth dialog is the first time the player talks to him after returning Shen to his father. The seventh dialog is the first time the player talks to him after bringing Shen and Rahasia to the Jedi Enclave. The eighth dialog is the first time the player talks to him after Nurik accepts Shen and Rahasia. The ninth dialog are subsequent conversations as a Padawan. The tenth dialog is a generic store opener linked throughout the other dialogs.

Exit stream 4: This conversation always has Crattis ask the player to bring him some crystals. DAN_DONE_CRATISL is set to true to show that the offer has been made. The end points of this conversation both link to stream 10.
Exit stream 5: This conversation links to stream 10.
Exit stream 6: This conversation links to stream 10. DAN_DONE_CRATISS is set to true to show that the romance has been mentioned.
